{
  "id": "S2P05M31",
  "title": {
    "product_var": "ZPRODTSK",
    "text": "HOW TO RECORD A KEY MACRO",
    "version_var": "ZSHRTVER",
    "prefix": "HELP"
  },
  "type": "help",
  "body": {
    "rows": [
      {
        "type": "command",
        "variable": "ZCMD"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Once we have filled in the fields, we simply need to hit the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "ENTER key to begin recorded the macro.  To re-emphasize that"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "macro recording is occuring, two indicators are set off:  first,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "a dual-tone beep sound is played over the PC speaker, and"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "secondly the word \"RECORDING\" is displayed on the status line"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "at the bottom of the screen."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "To abort from the macro naming panel without starting the macro"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "record, simply issue the CANCEL primary command."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Now, every key event that occurs is being recorded into the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "macro, including Backspaces, Enter-Key processing, PFKeys,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Mouse Events, Terminal functions, etc."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "(Press"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "ENTER+to continue)"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
